OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1780326668
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tue 16 Jun to Tue 30 Jun
OL,6,FThe start of the period is likely to
OL,7,Fbe relatively settled, with high
OL,8,Fpressure in the vicinity of the UK
OL,9,Fbringing drier conditions to most
OL,10,Fparts of the UK. However some showers
OL,11,For spells of rain are still possible.
OL,12,FWinds will mostly be light with
OL,13,Ftemperatures probably above normal.
OL,14,FTowards the end of June, low pressure
OL,15,Fmay begin to have more of an
OL,16,Finfluence, especially across the south
OL,17,Fwhere heavy showers and thunderstorms
OL,18,Fbecome more probable. It may also
OL,19,Fbecome hot in parts of the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
